{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"1\n    \n      Flash / Error Glimpse on Load\n      Root cause: The splash screen calls st.set_page_config(), then time.sleep(3), then st.rerun(). During the rerun, the page config switches (centered → wide or vice versa), and Streamlit briefly shows unstyled content or layout shift before the login page renders. The 2-cycle cookie check in auth_ui.py also causes an extra flash — cycle 1 shows a loading screen, cycle 2 checks cookies, potentially cycle 3 shows login.\n      Fix: Eliminate layout config switching, smoother splash→login transition","choice":"flash","id":null,"timestamp":1775126434453}
